# 👶 Baby Detection, Tracking & Alert System (YOLOv5 + YouTube Integration)

<p align="center">
  <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/800x250.png?text=Baby+Detection+%26+Alert+System" alt="Baby Detection Banner" width="700">
</p>

---

## 📌 Overview
This project uses **YOLOv5** to **detect, track, and alert** when a baby moves outside a **predefined safety zone**.

### Supports:
- 🎥 **Real-time webcam monitoring**  
- 📂 **Local video file analysis**  
- 📺 **YouTube video integration**  

---

## 🚀 Features
✅ **Custom-trained YOLOv5 model for baby detection**  
✅ **Tracking & real-time safety zone alerts**  
✅ **YouTube video download & processing**  
✅ **Google Colab friendly**  

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack
| Tool/Library | Purpose |
|--------------|---------|
| **Python 3** | Programming Language |
| **YOLOv5**   | Object Detection |
| **PyTorch**  | Deep Learning |
| **OpenCV**   | Video Processing |
| **yt-dlp**   | YouTube Download |
| **Pygame**   | Sound Alerts |

---

## ⚙️ Setup & Usage (Google Colab)

### 1️⃣ Clone YOLOv5
```bash
!git clone https://github.com/ultralytics/yolov5
%cd yolov5
!pip install -r requirements.txt
````

### 2️⃣ Download YouTube Video

```python
from yt_dlp import YoutubeDL

video_url = "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EISMLMybScA&t=4s"
ydl_opts = {"format": "best[ext=mp4]", "outtmpl": "baby_video.mp4"}
with YoutubeDL(ydl_opts) as ydl:
    ydl.download([video_url])
```

### 3️⃣ Run Detection + Alert

```bash
python detect_and_alert.py --weights best.pt --source baby_video.mp4
```

---

## 📊 Detection Box Colors

| Color   | Meaning                               |
| ------- | ------------------------------------- |
| 🟦 Blue | Baby inside safety zone               |
| 🟥 Red  | Baby outside safety zone (**Alert!**) |

